<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563820>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 1. Majority-rule consensus tree of species sampled from across the Cynipini, based on a Bayesian analysis of a concatenation of three loci (cytochrome b, long-wavelength opsin, and the D2 region of the 28S rRNA gene). Black stars at nodes indicate ±95% posterior probability support; white stars indicate 70%-94% posterior probability support. The revised limits of the genus Kokkocynips are indicated by the grey shaded box." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4563820/files/figure.png" .

